The other day, Kagege used
his faint presence to sneak
aboard the Uzushio, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100111_02_msg0002

And there, Kagege found what looked
like a good Salvage Point, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100111_02_msg0003

It's a hidden spot that even the salvagers
in Goldmund haven't noticed, so Kagege
is sure to find something good, mo.
